{"tid":1332310,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"721雙星報喜！","createTime":"2019-07-19T09:10:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-19T09:43:31.000Z","uid":183576,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"4b3d1d636135db72e0cec70bc994da8d0f743b72","tid":1332310,"uid":183576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T09:10:30.000Z","msg":"<pre><code data-type=\"\">民陣於本周日7.21再次發起反送中大遊行，並於今日收到警方不反對通知書，遊行原定以中環遮打道終審法院為終點，但警方以公共秩序安全為由，嚴格限制遊行終點必須設於灣仔盧押道與莊士敦道交界，不能以金鐘或中環作終站；且當日遊行必須於當晚9點結束，有別於過往定於晚上11時59分。警方也企硬只開放軒尼詩道西行3線及兩條電車路，拒絕開放軒尼詩道6條行車線。\nhttps://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190719/59840971?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post</code></pre><br />\n<br />\n既然係咁，大家不如諗下灣銅雙響？金鐘擺明被封(其實佢封唔封我理撚得佢咩，但咁就聚唔到多人)，地利人和都不利我方<br />\n但灣銅兩地都有好靚嘅地勢，後者仲要多支那人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />而且對家應該冇演練過呢兩個地點，我覺得兩度同時開花會幾靚<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n721 be water，遍地開花永不凋零！各位手足後日見<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae1d66d19779765604cf03ac028fd846aad6099f","tid":1332310,"uid":78222,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T09:12:06.000Z","msg":"姐係助攻我地銅鑼灣shopping嘆冷氣啦<br />\n金鐘又多監控燈柱又小市民 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c97ddb0296cff367ff4bfde575caf87862589a6","tid":1332310,"uid":265314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T09:12:52.000Z","msg":"721金鐘"},{"pid":"62e5dd41b8c1d92b887a757298d9ed492775be34","tid":1332310,"uid":128569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T09:15:44.000Z","msg":"冷靜啲 佢叫得你地係灣仔 預左有野搞 一定會有部署 唔好咁輕鬆"},{"pid":"74f5dccb2564d8ea16e2eb909763b6cdde4a2c72","tid":1332310,"uid":183576,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6c97ddb0296cff367ff4bfde575caf87862589a6","tid":1332310,"uid":265314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T09:12:52.000Z","msg":"721金鐘"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T09:17:22.000Z","msg":"金鐘難聚人呀ching，未必贏到<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e71213ee7b20ea3e778db8425df8ebbbeeeb1dd8","tid":1332310,"uid":183576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"62e5dd41b8c1d92b887a757298d9ed492775be34","tid":1332310,"uid":128569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T09:15:44.000Z","msg":"冷靜啲 佢叫得你地係灣仔 預左有野搞 一定會有部署 唔好咁輕鬆"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T09:17:44.000Z","msg":"但老銅<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95116fb841c400af92b150c254b5da155894152a","tid":1332310,"uid":183576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T09:27:27.000Z","msg":"721不見不散"},{"pid":"cbf97fad458b3c4633a1688fc28333d1879fce1c","tid":1332310,"uid":183576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T09:43:31.000Z","msg":"721721721"}]}